- What's up, buddy?

246
00:15:06,884 --> 00:15:08,613
Okay. Later, dudes.

247
00:15:09,554 --> 00:15:11,078
Radical.

248
00:15:32,043 --> 00:15:35,638
Dude, look where I'm standing.
I'm standing where Z stood.

249
00:15:37,415 --> 00:15:41,249
- Aw, man.
- Dude, you gotta try this.

250
00:15:41,419 --> 00:15:43,979
- No, I'm okay.
- Come on. Just one bite.

251
00:15:44,155 --> 00:15:46,487
All right. One bite, that's it.

252
00:15:47,858 --> 00:15:49,587
Yeah, yeah? What do you think?

253
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:52,024
It's not bad.
It kind of tastes like chicken...

254
00:15:52,463 --> 00:15:54,363
Yep. What's chi-chi?

255
00:15:54,699 --> 00:15:57,759
Coming through! Oh, crap.

256
00:16:03,074 --> 00:16:05,542
Oh, man. I'm in love.

257
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:08,770
Help me! I'm drowning!

258
00:16:12,016 --> 00:16:15,747
What are you standing here
next to me for? Go talk to her, man.

259
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,945
- I'm not gonna talk to her.
- She's digging on you.

260
00:16:18,122 --> 00:16:19,214
- She called you crap.
- Joe.

261
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:21,324
- Thanks again.
- All right, well...

262
00:16:21,492 --> 00:16:23,756
...this is the third time
you've been unconscious this week.

263
00:16:23,928 --> 00:16:25,759
I just don't think
it's very good for your brain.

264
00:16:25,930 --> 00:16:28,490
- I know. Bye, Lani.
- Okay.

265
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:32,160
Yeah, that was awesome
how you saved his life and all.

266
00:16:32,336 --> 00:16:35,965
That was just unbelievable. Really.

267
00:16:37,842 --> 00:16:40,367
You here for the surf contest?

268
00:16:41,145 --> 00:16:45,343
- Well, I'll be watching you.
- Really? You'll be watching me?

269
00:16:45,516 --> 00:16:47,143
Well, yeah,
from the lifeguard station.

270
00:16:47,318 --> 00:16:49,616
- Yeah. Right.
- It's my job.

271
00:16:49,787 --> 00:16:51,914
- That's your job.
- Are you gonna kiss her?

272
00:16:52,089 --> 00:16:54,114
- What's going on?
- Come on, Joe.

273
00:16:54,292 --> 00:16:56,556
- You were saying you were in love...
- No, I didn't say that.

274
00:16:56,727 --> 00:16:58,422
- Look, he really digs you.
- Joe, listen...

275
00:16:58,596 --> 00:17:00,757
He likes you, though. See you.

276
00:17:00,931 --> 00:17:03,024
I love my job.
I have an amazing job.

277
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,565
Just this week, with the contest...

278
00:17:06,170 --> 00:17:09,571
...it's a little crazy. You really
have to be extra, extra attentive.

279
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:12,934
When you have so many guys
in the water you can't miss a thing.

280
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:16,773
But you know what? I have a perfect
record. I've never lost anybody.

281
00:17:16,981 --> 00:17:19,006
Sure, there have been
close calls, but...

282
00:17:19,183 --> 00:17:21,777
- Help!
- Oh, Arnold. I turn my back for one...

283
00:17:21,952 --> 00:17:24,284
- Just lay some feeling on her.
