295
00:18:16,340 --> 00:18:17,329
Great shot!

296
00:18:17,508 --> 00:18:18,975
What? Hey!

297
00:18:19,577 --> 00:18:22,410
- Every time.
- He's got a pretty good throwing fin.

298
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,741
Stop doing... Stop it! Cut it out!

299
00:18:25,516 --> 00:18:28,417
- That's like three in a row.
- Here, give it a shot.

300
00:18:30,755 --> 00:18:34,987
What? Wait a minute. Look at this.

301
00:18:35,159 --> 00:18:37,593
- Don't. Stop it.
- It's a Big Z necklace.

302
00:18:37,762 --> 00:18:40,822
That's not funny. Stop.
Stop! What are you doing?

303
00:18:40,998 --> 00:18:43,125
Look, everybody, it's Big Z's last fan!

304
00:18:43,334 --> 00:18:45,199
Coming through.
Out of the way. Let's go.

305
00:18:45,369 --> 00:18:47,360
- You don't deserve to talk about him.
- He's a big zero.

306
00:18:47,538 --> 00:18:49,028
- Shut your mouth!
- Zero starts with "Z"!

307
00:18:49,206 --> 00:18:52,039
You'll never be
as good as Big Z, Stank.

308
00:18:53,177 --> 00:18:56,738
Hey, hey, people, come on now.
Smile on your brother.

309
00:18:56,914 --> 00:19:01,248
- Keep your girlfriend out of this!
- You can't do that to my friend.

310
00:19:01,986 --> 00:19:04,921
You're getting quite a workout there.
That feels good.

311
00:19:05,089 --> 00:19:08,581
Why don't you work on my glutes
